{"tid":1766040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"投考 AO、EO 人數急跌","createTime":"2019-12-02T09:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T19:23:42.000Z","uid":230825,"like":27,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"111ea87bd4c9268f40ab5e951bcd6718463e0636","tid":1766040,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/ZkEQLN?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FZkEQLN%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=04f86ca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/ZkEQLN?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n據星島日報報道，在抗爭運動下，以往「爭崩頭」的鐵飯碗政府職位，包括政務主任職系，申請人數減少約 3000 人，即是跌兩成，平均 267 人爭一個位。另外，警察招募以新口號作招徠，包括「如果您想保護香港這個家」&mdash; 榮譽、心繫社會，使命等。<br />\n<br />\n今年度申請政務主任職系人數相較 2018/19 年度跌兩成，有 1萬 2000 人。二級行政主任職系申請人數比上年度大減 4000 人，共 1 萬 9000 人，跌幅 18%。報道指，AO 及 EO 的申請人數創了「佔中運動」後的新低，跟政府形象長期低落有關。<br />\n警隊今個財政年度目標是招募 1815 名警務人員，當中見習督察 195 名，警員 1620 名，另外輔警警員 320 名。6月以來，警民衝突持續升級，警察不時舉行的 4 點鐘記者亦不見改善到崩緊的警民關係，警方在招募時，亦側重迎難而上、忠誠、肩負使命等口號及理念。四款新的口號分別是：「如果您想保護香港這個家」&mdash; 榮譽、心繫社會，使命；「如果您想守護香港」 &mdash; 撲滅罪行、忠誠、肩負使命；「如果您想維護法紀」 &mdash; 執法、繩之於法、滅罪；「如果您想並肩前行」 &mdash; 堅定不移、勇毅、迎難而上。<br />\n除了招新人，警方亦計劃招募大約 1000 名退休警務人員「回巢」幫手處理警務工作，首批將於本月重返警隊，當中部分曾是總督察級別，部分會加入刑事或軍裝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4cb110d74b4cdd156c2042a3236980b0733f20","tid":1766040,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0850be27e3288a5054a21dda33cbfdaa3d42a27a","tid":1766040,"uid":21920,"like":36,"dislike":7,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"入得去仲會幫你咩<br />\n成為高牆一方"},{"pid":"7b54f6624b0f63b906c219bc4915b9f69fa1238f","tid":1766040,"uid":321345,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"你不如話考狗隊<br />\n睇下到時會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0e4875f79e615ec7a320ef1c663a9590c23b82","tid":1766040,"uid":165683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"考入去 Please"},{"pid":"c1ffb0cd05b2bd4ddc7dcea48b606c02b83c6e0b","tid":1766040,"uid":303463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"良知問題 依家咁既政府仲點滲透"},{"pid":"9c3bb08b86fc86cf65572a18293c4c537d53a269","tid":1766040,"uid":165683,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"0850be27e3288a5054a21dda33cbfdaa3d42a27a","tid":1766040,"uid":21920,"like":36,"dislike":7,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"入得去仲會幫你咩<br />\n成為高牆一方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"on 9<br />\nAO 主流黃<br />\n之前有幾百聯署"},{"pid":"2126e405623cb6afd811d07cfd6c550b9cebd367","tid":1766040,"uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1ffb0cd05b2bd4ddc7dcea48b606c02b83c6e0b","tid":1766040,"uid":303463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"良知問題 依家咁既政府仲點滲透"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"AO 主流黃<br />\n之前有幾百聯署"},{"pid":"bb8747ef337ec3423c2d4211546110806f13114d","tid":1766040,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"分分鐘去唔到美國wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25ba30ebe2a57793195bfb2bd8fa56967ff0869","tid":1766040,"uid":105578,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"唔係應該大量人加入政府同紀律部隊咩(除咗黑警)，有番啲牽制力量係入邊好似好啲"},{"pid":"e1f69984fcb1602c00df258de438837fd8ed5a4c","tid":1766040,"uid":55851,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"EO都算<br />\n做AO除非成世唔升，否則做到中年分分鐘比人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781153445a540f2a374c3e10047600687b346a31","tid":176