分曾是總督察級別，部分會加入刑事或軍裝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"74207a1dbfc7f4045761a6c84093cec824c801f9","tid":1766040,"uid":230825,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"到時啲EO同AO全部都係大陸仔嘅時候你哋就知味道啦"},{"pid":"c89fa0bd728487b92ac7c3922ee9b464a9349867","tid":1766040,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b1359fa4ec85a5a4a9e585affc7c39baeb531f","tid":1766040,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f68fdb425a98283b8d9d2debc66d12831029bee","tid":1766040,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"老燒話哩幾年唔請本地大學生<br />\n咁係嚴重歧視<br />\n應該叫議員質問 + 要求公布6月至今請咗既人中<br />\n畢業地區分布"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚信條廢老喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"質問吓冇壞既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9646b4ddbeedcaf55d552db387934afd7a090295","tid":1766040,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"投考警察人數有冇急跌？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"f0b3878da0dc0a5b00622c6b3e3c79360689608c","tid":1766040,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"仲考<br />\n分分鐘淨係可以返大灣區退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd0cdcfd207f0f2b7742d036d01fa52f2385f0b","tid":1766040,"uid":54579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2126e405623cb6afd811d07cfd6c550b9cebd367","tid":1766040,"uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1ffb0cd0